title: Abdelhaq Nadir
text: Abdelhaq Nadir (born 15 June 1993) is a Moroccan <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. He competed in the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%202020%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20lightweight">men's lightweight event</a> at the <a href="2020%20Summer%20Olympics">2020 Summer Olympics</a>.
